Vivian Sternwood is the elder of General Sternwood's wild daughters. Vivian is seductive but dangerous, a beautiful and smart temptress whose dark eyes hide many secrets. She is a gambler and a drinker and an accomplice to murder. Vivian is a spoiled brat who always gets her way, and she is capable of cruelty. Nevertheless, it is possible that she has murdered her husband all to keep her father, General Sternwood, from the pain of the truth.